reButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526123\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526123\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 14, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bmj1665703279605.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bmj1665703279605.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bmj1665703279605.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bmj1665703279605\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">Error: No SQL generated, /genSql does not support driver option\n            <var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Option&gt;</var> as specified in the assignment file,\n         [DRIVER_SETTINGS], USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;DB&gt;</var>_PARAMS.</samp>\n</h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A connector option specified for the target DBMS is not supported by\n         <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/gensql</span>. For example, if you specified <code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ORA_params = upgrade\n         packages</code>, no create table scripts are generated.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__section_N1002C_N10029_N10001\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1153048e64\">Explanation</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__p_d153050e1_d153051e1_d153052e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/gensql</span> command does not support deprecated connector options that were used in older versions of Uniface when upgrading an existing table rather than creating new tables.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__li_d53027e1_d53028e1_d53029e1\">Oracle (ORA): <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade\n               packages</span></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__li_d53030e1_d53031e1_d53032e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__p_d153056e1_d153057e1_d153058e1\">Sybase (SYB):</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__li_d53033e1_d53034e1_d53035e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade</span></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__li_d53036e1_d53037e1_d53038e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade dpl</span></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__li_d53039e1_d53040e1_d53041e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade apl</span></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__li_d53042e1_d53043e1_d53044e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade locks</span></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmj1665703279605__li_d53045e1_d53046e1_d53047e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade procs</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cck1665702542032.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/genSql</a><p>The /genSql switch generates DBMS-specific SQL command scripts for preparing an application database or the Uniface Repository, including creating tables and enforcing referential integrity constraints in the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526123\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526123\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Error: No SQL generated, /genSql does not support driver option <Option> as specified in the assignment file, [DRIVER_SETTINGS], USYS$<DB>_PARAMS. Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 14, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Error: No SQL generated, /genSql does not support driver option <Option> as specified in the assignment file, [DRIVER_SETTINGS], USYS$ <DB> _PARAMS. A connector option specified for the target DBMS is not supported by /gensql . For example, if you specified USYS$ORA_params = upgrade packages , no create table scripts are generated. Explanation The /gensql command does not support deprecated connector options that were used in older versions of Uniface when upgrading an existing table rather than creating new tables. Oracle (ORA): upgrade packages Sybase (SYB): upgrade upgrade dpl upgrade apl upgrade locks upgrade procs Related Links /genSql The /genSql switch generates DBMS-specific SQL command scripts for preparing an application database or the Uniface Repository, including creating tables and enforcing referential integrity constraints in the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}